headline: T-Mobile Wins Network Experience Three-peat
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., January 09, 2025--The Un-carrier has locked in the three-peat! Opensignal’s latest Mobile Network Experience report has once again found T-Mobile’s network performs the best in overall experience categories with even more wins for 5G download speeds, 5G coverage experience, 5G availability, consistent quality experience and was unbeaten for reliability experience.
